Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:06.94,sign_75_1_It_was_raining__,,0,0,0,,It was raining...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:05.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,It was raining...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.58,0:00:05.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,﻿雨がふっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:11.65,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,You're always reading that book, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.69,0:00:11.68,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもその本を読んでるな　坊主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.93,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,Is it that interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:14.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなに面白いか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:16.58,Stray Dogs - Flashback,BoyO,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:16.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,面白い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:18.46,Stray Dogs - Flashback,BoyO,0,0,0,,I've read it many times now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.81,0:00:18.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もう何度も読んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:24.03,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな話より面白い話が世の中にはごまんとあるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:22.01,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,There are so many more \Nstories out in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:24.20,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,that are far more interesting \Nthan what's in that book.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:27.37,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,Where's Part Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:27.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その本　下巻はどうした
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:34.93,sign_668_10_Part_2_of_3_,Sign,0,0,0,,Part 2 of 3
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,下巻は持ってない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:30.10,Stray Dogs - Flashback,BoyO,0,0,0,,I don't have Part Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:32.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら探してもなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:32.52,Stray Dogs - Flashback,BoyO,0,0,0,,I've looked and looked, \Nbut I've never found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:34.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それで得心がいったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:34.92,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,Now it all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:39.33,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,That story's Part Three is \Nthe worst of the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.67,0:00:39.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その小説は下巻がとんでもなく最悪でな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:42.76,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,You should consider yourself satisfied \Nwith just the first two parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.88,0:00:42.80,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,上巻と中巻だけで満足しておけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:45.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それがお前の為だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:45.28,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,I'm saying this for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:47.20,Stray Dogs - Flashback,BoyO,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:47.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうもいかない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.49,0:00:49.61,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,Then you write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:49.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ならばお前が書け
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:52.80,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,自分が書く？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:52.81,Stray Dogs - Flashback,BoyO,0,0,0,,Me, write?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:57.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それが唯一その小説を完璧なままにしておく方法だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:57.82,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,That's the only way you can \Nkeep that story perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:01:06.04,sign_668_10_Part_2_of_3_,Sign,0,0,0,,Part 2 of 3
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.90,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,小説を書くことは人間を書くことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.55,0:01:01.95,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,To write a story is \Nto write about a person,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:05.89,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どう生きて　どう死ぬべきかということをな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:05.84,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,and how that person should live and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:10.27,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,From what I've seen, \Nyou have the qualifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:10.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,儂の見たところ　お前にはその資格がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.69,0:01:12.84,Stray Dogs - Flashback,BoyO,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:12.90,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたはいったい誰なんです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:14.48,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:14.42,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,儂か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:18.06,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:17.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,儂の名は…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.60,0:01:28.56,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Are you awake, Odasaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:28.87,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,目覚めたかい　織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:31.67,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:31.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,気分は？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:34.79,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm experiencing \Nall the hangovers I'll have
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:37.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,向こう五十年の二日酔いをまとめて受け取っている気分だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:37.32,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,in the next fifty years \Nall at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.81,0:01:42.24,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I saw Ango at the place you told me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:42.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前に云われた場所で　安吾に会った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.71,0:01:45.37,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,So Ango was there, like I suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,矢張り安吾はあの場所にいたのだね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:47.09,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:47.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:52.27,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,He vanished into the dark \Nwith soldiers in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:52.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,黒ずくめの兵士達と闇に消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.80,0:01:57.69,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Sounds like black special ops.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:57.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,差し当たり　黒の特殊部隊といったところだね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:02.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやら起こっている現象は二つに分けられるようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:02.90,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It seems recent events can be \Ndivided into two categories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:05.72,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Are they a separate organization from Mimic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:06.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,奴らとミミックは別組織なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.07,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,They're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,別だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:11.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ　黒の特殊部隊のほうは当面無視していい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:11.55,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,But we can pretty much ignore the \Nblack special ops guys for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:14.06,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Mimic is the more dangerous enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:13.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,矢張り危険なのはミミックだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:21.55,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,市内で起きている抗争に　芥川君を初めとする武闘派構成員で対抗しているけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:18.56,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Akutagawa-kun and other \Ncombat squad members
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:21.61,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,are dealing with conflicts in the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:26.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらは敵の長が使う異能力さえわかっていないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:26.11,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,but we don't even know what the \Nenemy leader's ability is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:27.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,分が悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:27.54,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,We're at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:32.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その芥川という男は確かお前の部下だったな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:32.20,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,That Akutagawa is one of your \Nsubordinates, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:36.00,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I heard his ability has high \Noffensive capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.57,0:02:36.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,かなり攻撃的な異能力を持っていると聞いたが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:38.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼は鞘のない刀剣だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:38.59,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,He's a naked sword without a scabbard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:42.37,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll become the strongest \Ngifted mafia member in the near future but,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:42.42,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,遠からずマフィア最強の異能力者になるだろうが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:46.49,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,right now, he needs someone to \Nteach him how to sheathe his blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:46.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今は誰かが刃の仕舞い方を教えなくちゃならない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:48.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,話が逸れたね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.01,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Sorry, that was a tangent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:52.26,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,This morning, the council of five \Ntop executives convened.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:52.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今朝　五大幹部会が招集され
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:57.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ポートマフィアの全戦力を以て　ミミックを迎撃することが決定された
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:54.68,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,They made a decision to attack Mimic
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.65,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,with everything \Nthe Port Mafia can muster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.31,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:02.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,つい先刻　芥川君を含む私の部下が奇襲を受け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.32,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,my subordinates, including Akutagawa-kun,\N were hit by a surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:04.19,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,They're still fighting at the art museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今も美術館で抗争を…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:06.42,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:06.42,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Odasaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:08.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか行くのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.41,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You're not serious about going, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:11.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,全戦力を以て迎撃するんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:11.45,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,We're hitting them with \Neverything we've got, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:16.46,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd be interested in conflict, since you don't kill people.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:16.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人殺しをしない織田作は抗争なんて興味ないと思っていたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:17.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:17.42,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.48,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあなんで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:19.52,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Then why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:23.19,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I've acquired a lot of debts in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.89,0:03:23.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,借りの多い人生だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:27.50,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,部下が苦戦中なら　扶けが必要だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.10,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,If your subordinates are in a tough spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.47,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,they need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:34.27,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You should forget about your debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:34.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,借りなんて忘れてしまえばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:41.45,sign_5148_68_Episode_15___Som,Sign 0336,0,0,0,,Episode 15 \N Some Day in a \NRoom with a \NSeaside View
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:40.92,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,No one remembers what you owe to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:40.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,相手だって　何を貸したかなんて　覚えちゃいないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,銃など愚者の戎具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Guns are the weapons of fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:10.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,All too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:10.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりにも非力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:15.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Gide,0,0,0,,So you're the one they speak of... \NThe gifted one in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:11.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴君か
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,黒衣の異能力者と云うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.21,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,My name is Gide.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:24.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,乃公の名はジイド　ミミックを束ねる者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.56,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I am the leader of Mimic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:29.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,雑魚を何人倒そうと　あの人は僕を認めぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:29.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,He will never acknowledge me, \Nno matter how many underlings I defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:31.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,手合わせ願おう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:31.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,I'd like to challenge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:33.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一つ聞く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:33.65,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:40.04,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Is your ability sufficient to release \Nour souls from original sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:40.06,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴君の異能力は我らの魂を原罪から解放するに足る力か
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:41.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Want to find out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,試してみるか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:45.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.63,0:04:45.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,逃すか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:50.84,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,It seems you are not the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴君ではないようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:57.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.03,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,莫迦な
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Is this an ability?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:59.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これは異能力か
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:00.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:00.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:03.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Can you read my moves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の動きが読めるとでもいうのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.16,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,In a few more years,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:28.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あと数年もあれば　我々の望みを叶える異能力者になっていたやもしれぬが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:28.14,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,you may have grown powerful\N enough to grant our wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:29.87,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,but we cannot wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:29.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,待てぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:31.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,殺せ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:31.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Defeat means death.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,敗残兵は去るのみ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:38.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,I regret that I could not \Nbe the enemy you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:38.47,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様の求める敵になってやれず　すまなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:40.38,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:40.40,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,さらばだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,足を撃たれたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.34,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Did you get shot in the leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:55.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:55.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:57.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様　何をする
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:57.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:00.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,降ろせ　降ろせ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Let me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:00.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は織田作之助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.29,0:06:02.79,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I'm Oda Sakunosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.77,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I heard about you from \NDazai and came to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:05.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰に話を聞いて扶けに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:20.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様の名は太宰さんから聞いている
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,I've heard of you from Dazai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:23.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,You're one of the lower-ranking members.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:23.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一介の下級構成員だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:24.97,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:25.02,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:28.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてあの人の友人だと聞いた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:28.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,And I heard you're a friend to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,誠か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:35.03,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その手の言葉は軽々しく口にしない主義だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:34.99,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I have a policy of not using \Nthat word lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰さんは云った
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:37.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Dazai-san said
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:41.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は百年経っても貴様には勝てぬと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.24,0:06:41.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,I wouldn't stand a chance against you,\N not in a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:43.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間割れをしている時間はない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.74,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Now's not the time to be having a falling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:48.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Why doesn't Dazai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:49.06,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故太宰さんは僕を
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:52.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Aku,0,0,0,,Are you the same?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様も…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:54.96,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:55.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前に期待している友の為にも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:57.84,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I have to bring you back,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:00.73,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,especially for a friend who \Nhas high hopes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.76,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,必ず連れて帰らねばならん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:06.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,予感があった
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:06.60,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I did have a premonition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.36,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何の話だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:13.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この国で　その異能力者に会えるという予感だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:13.36,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I had a premonition that I'd be able to \Nmeet the person I seek in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,乃公はジイド
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:14.96,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I am Gide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:19.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,我ら幽霊の魂を解き放つ者を探しに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:19.72,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I came here in search of the one who can \Nrelease the souls of ghosts like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:24.20,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,知人の葬儀業者なら　割引料金で紹介できるが
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:24.16,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I can get you a discount with an \Nundertaker I know if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.97,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,必要ない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:26.05,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,There is no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:28.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,たった今見つけたからな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:28.54,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I just found the one we were looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:41.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:41.79,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.39,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:47.44,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I haven't even fired a single round.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.47,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,乃公はまだ銃を撃ってすらいないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:48.72,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:48.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何をした
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:53.38,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I just saw a future where you \Nwould dodge to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:53.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,乃公には今　貴君が右に避ける未来が観えた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それに合わせて狙いを修正した
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:56.33,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Therefore, I adjusted my aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:08:00.36,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だが貴君はその未来を観て方向を修正した
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.48,0:08:00.42,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,But you saw that future, \Nso you adjusted as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:02.97,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Which I also saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それも乃公には観えた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:06.98,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,The ability to see a few seconds into the \Nfuture if you are to be in any danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,数秒後に起こる自分の危機を観る能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:10.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,乃公もまた貴君と同じことができる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:10.87,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I can do what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:14.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺達の持つ未来観測能力は万能だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.39,0:08:14.91,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,The predictive ability \Nwe have is omnipotent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:19.66,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,You are the only one who can \Nkill me and end this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:19.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴君だけが乃公を葬り　この抗争を止められる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:22.81,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,If you are one of the Port Mafia,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:25.97,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴君がポートマフィアの人間なら　敵の長たる乃公を撃つことこそ本懐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:26.05,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,killing me, the enemy leader, \Nmust be your greatest desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:27.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,断る
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:27.85,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.97,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I'm only here to help one of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:31.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は仲間を扶けに来ただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.15,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.74,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,You're not one of the mafia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:34.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴君はマフィアではないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.90,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,マフィアも色々だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:36.81,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,There are different types in the mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:39.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,銃は人を殺す道具だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:39.48,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Guns are tools for murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.87,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,And this is a war zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてここは戦場だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,戦うことに興味がない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.31,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:45.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,な…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:49.25,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,What I'm interested in is living.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:49.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が興味があるのは　生きることだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:52.04,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,There is nothing more important \Nin life than death!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:52.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,死よりも重要な生など存在しない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.97,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　それでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:12.11,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Good, that's how it should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:13.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:13.61,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:19.78,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Are you refusing to fight me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:19.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あくまで本気で戦う心算はないと
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:22.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺には殺しをしない理由がある
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.67,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,There is a reason I don't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:24.41,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Look elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:24.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,余所を当たってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:25.41,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:30.45,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,My subordinates and I have been \Nwandering the whole world like ghosts,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:33.79,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,乃公と部下達は死に値する場所を求め　死霊のように世界を彷徨った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:33.66,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,looking for a place worthy of our deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:36.68,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,You are our only wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:36.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴君が唯一の望みなのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,戦ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.46,0:09:38.73,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:39.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,でなければ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:40.02,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,If you refuse—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:42.46,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺がお前の願いを聞けないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:42.43,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,The reason I can't do as you wish
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:44.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,夢があるからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.19,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,is because I have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:50.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いつかポートマフィアを辞めて　何でもできる身になった時
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:49.98,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Some day when I can quit the \NPort Mafia and become a free man,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:54.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,海の見える部屋で　机に座って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:54.78,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I want to sit down at a desk in a room \Nwhere I can see the sea, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:09:59.01,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,Then you write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:59.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ならばお前が書け
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:03.59,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,That's the only way you can \Nkeep that story perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:03.56,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それが唯一その小説を完璧にしておく方法だ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:07.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,小説家になりたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.20,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I want to become a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.41,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I want to throw the gun aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:11.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,銃を捨て　紙とペンだけを持って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.52,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,and only have pen and paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:18.05,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,One man told me that to write \Na story is to write a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:18.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ある人が「小説を書くことは人間を書くことだ」と云った
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:22.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人の命を奪う者に人生を書くことはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:22.51,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,A man who takes lives \Ncannot write about lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.21,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,That's why I won't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:25.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だから俺は人を殺さない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:29.93,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,And that's the reason why you \Nrefuse to enter our battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:29.97,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それが我々の戦場に登ってこない理由なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:32.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それがお前の答えか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:32.38,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,So that's your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:34.73,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.93,0:10:34.76,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.12,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:53.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.16,0:10:55.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,防弾内衣か
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.22,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,A bullet-proof vest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:58.55,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,生きているが故の痛みだな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:58.57,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,That pain that is a privilege of the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:01.83,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,It's something we lost long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.28,0:11:01.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,とうの昔に失ったものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:04.84,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,We are already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:04.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,我らはもう死んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:09.63,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,We're just soulless husks \Nbeing controlled by ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:09.68,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,魂のない肉体を　亡霊が操っているに過ぎない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.18,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は死んでいない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.14,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,You're not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:15.01,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened \Nto you in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:14.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,過去に何があったか知らないが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:18.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の死に方をゆっくり考えることはできる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:18.77,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,but you can still think \Nabout how you want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.77,0:11:20.07,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Why won't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故わからない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:22.25,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,You are the only...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:22.19,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴君だけが唯一の…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴君は乃公を殺さない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:28.98,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,You will not kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:31.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,乃公の望みを理解していないからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.90,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,That's because you don't understand my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:35.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そして乃公も今は貴君を殺さない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.56,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,And I won't kill you right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:40.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴君だけが我らを浄火の戦場に導く者だからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:40.11,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,because you are the only one who can guide \Nus to the battlefield of purification.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:44.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴君に本当の我らを理解させてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:44.40,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,I will make you understand \Nwho we really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうすればわかるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:47.26,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,Then you will understand
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:51.65,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,that, between the two of us, \Nthere can be only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:51.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貴君と乃公のどちらかが死ぬしかないということが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:55.15,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,You should look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:55.11,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しみにしていろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:13:21.98,Stray Dogs - Default,G,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:26.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,夜はいい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.04,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,The night is a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:29.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,マフィアの時間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:29.09,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It's a time that belongs to the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:31.23,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これからどうする
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:33.56,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたもんかねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:33.71,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:36.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それにしても災難だったね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:36.28,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That was quite some trouble \Nyou got into, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:40.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の首領に会うなり　熱烈な求愛を受けるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:38.50,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Who would've thought that the enemy leader
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.00,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,you'd just met would turn \Ninto such an earnest suitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:46.89,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,They're weird, looking for war so that they \Ncan find a place worthy of their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:46.84,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,死に値する場所を探す為に戦場を求めるなど　変な奴らだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:47.92,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうかい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:48.11,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:52.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,死に方に工夫を凝らしたいなんて　私にはない発想だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:52.86,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Their wish to be creative about their deaths \Nis something I hadn't thought about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.22,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,How long will this conflict last?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この抗争はいつまで続く
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.62,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Mimic's soldiers aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:14:01.06,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ミミックの兵士はともかく　指揮官の異能力は厄介だね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.75,0:14:01.14,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,their leader's ability is a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:02.87,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,奇襲が効かない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:02.93,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Surprise attacks won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:06.18,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That means we need inside info.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:06.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,となると　内部情報が必要だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.29,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Any leads you can think of?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,心当たりはあるかい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.36,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Only Ango.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:11.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾しかいない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:13.56,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:13.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私も同意見だね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.02,0:14:16.82,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's some \Nway we can find Ango.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:16.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾を探す方法はないものかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.36,0:14:18.12,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:18.18,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ある
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:19.65,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,There is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:19.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.37,0:14:23.28,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,To be more precise,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:25.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,正確に云えば　探し出す必要すらない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.76,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,there is no need to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.26,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:28.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ここか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:31.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,他にあるかい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:31.11,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Where else?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:39.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,やあ　どうも
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:39.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I started without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:41.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お先にやってますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:48.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,連絡くらいくれてもよかったんじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.68,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,You could've called.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:51.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I had a hard time losing my tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:51.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,尾行を撒くのに苦労しましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,But today's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:55.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,でも今日は大丈夫です　ゆっくり飲める
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I can spend as much time as I want here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:57.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:59.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それで　どうしてここがわかったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:14:59.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,How'd you know to find me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.32,0:15:02.84,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Just a hunch, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.80,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なんとなく　ね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:05.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I'm lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:05.97,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕はついてる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:09.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I didn't think I could drink here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで飲めることはもうないと思っていました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:14.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,潜入捜査官にしては　随分と感傷的じゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:14.54,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You're pretty sentimental for a mole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:19.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君はポートマフィアに入る前から　別の顔があった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:19.65,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Even before you joined the Port Mafia, \Nyou had a different identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:25.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それは国の秘密機関　内務省異能特務課のエージェントとしての顔だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.95,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,And that's as a secret agent of the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.98,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You were an agent of the \NMinistry of Internal Affairs'
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.90,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,gifted special operations division.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:29.35,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Your mission was to monitor the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:29.36,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,任務はポートマフィアの動向の監視
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:33.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,国内の異能力者を統括する秘密組織といえど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:33.43,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Though the division oversees \Nall gifted within the nation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.86,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,should there ever be an all-out \Nwar with the Port Mafia,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.58,0:15:37.11,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ポートマフィアと全面戦争となれば　只では済まない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.20,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,the division will suffer heavy casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:41.46,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,The division's primary purpose is to \Nmanage, not annihilate, the gifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:41.40,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも特務課の任務は異能力者の管理だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,殲滅じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:49.09,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That's why they had an agent infiltrate the \NPort Mafia and monitor their movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:49.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だからポートマフィア内にエージェントを潜入させ　動向を監視させていた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:53.69,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Then Mimic came up at the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:53.68,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてそこに　ミミックの話が持ち上がった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:58.68,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,The gifted criminal organization \Nhad been planning to enter Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:16:01.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,日本上陸を計画していた異能犯罪組織は特務課からしても頭の痛い存在だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:01.38,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,They were a headache for the division,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:08.37,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,so the division decided to have you \Nmonitor Mimic... as the Port Mafia's spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:08.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-1}それで君にミミックの動向を探らせることにした　ポートマフィアの間諜としてね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.79,0:16:13.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,薄給の国家公務員としては　まったく割りに合わない仕事でしたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:11.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,As a lowly salaried government worker,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:13.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,it was a job entirely above my pay grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.06,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,So, in other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:16.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり安吾は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:21.46,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Ango wasn't a double agent, \Nbut a triple agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:21.40,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,二重間諜ではなく　三重間諜だったというわけか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:28.96,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Tell us about Mimic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:28.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ミミックについて教えてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:33.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I heard Gide and Odasaku-san traded blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:33.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ジイドと織田作さんが会敵したという情報が入りました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ジイドの異能力は見ましたか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.47,0:16:36.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Did you see Gide's ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:37.77,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.90,0:16:37.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,見た
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:41.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Gide is elusive, and his location \Nis never made known to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:41.46,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ジイドは神出鬼没で　居場所を悟らせません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:46.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,The brass intends to let the \NPort Mafia handle this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:46.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,上はこの件を　完全にポートマフィアに投げる腹積もりです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:49.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃあまた随分と虫のいい話だね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:49.45,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Well, that's very convenient for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:55.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,けどポートマフィアにしたって　あの異能力を突破するのは難しいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:55.26,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,But even the Port Mafia would have a \Nhard time dealing with his ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:56.78,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:56.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろん
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:17:01.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一人の最下級構成員を除いて　だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:01.04,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,that's if we don't consider a certain \Nlowest-ranking member in the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:07.50,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の異能力も奴の異能力もほんの数秒先が予見できるに過ぎない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:07.60,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Both our abilities only entail looking \Na few seconds into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.66,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,If push comes to shove,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:13.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,結局のところ　勝敗は戦闘と射撃の技倆にかかってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.81,0:17:13.00,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,the outcome will be dependent on \Nour skills in combat and shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:15.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,不確定要素は大きいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:15.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,The unknown variables will matter a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:18.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,There's also "the singularity \Nof the ability" to consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:18.84,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,異能力の特異点の問題もある
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.35,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,The singularity of the ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,異能力の特異点？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:27.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Didn't something unusual happen when \Nyou used your ability against Gide?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.80,0:17:27.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ジイドに対して異能力を使った時　いつもと違うことが起きませんでしたか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.91,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Yeah, it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.36,0:17:40.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　起きた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:43.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,複数の異能力が干渉し合うと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:47.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,The government has observed that \Nwhen some abilities interact,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:50.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ごく稀にまったく予想もしなかった方向に異能力が暴走するという現象が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.63,0:17:53.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,they may careen off into an entirely \Nunexpected direction in rare cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:53.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,政府機関に拠って確認されています
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:58.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I wasn't really supposed to tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:58.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今の話　本当はしてはいけないことになっています
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:04.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,It'd become a major issue if the brass were \Nto know that I am meeting you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:04.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕がこうして会っていることも　上層部に知られたら大問題になります
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:07.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I'll have to go underground \Nfor the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.56,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,当面は姿を隠さなくては
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:08.78,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おやおや
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:13.39,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You're talking as though you \Nwill leave this place alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:13.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで自分が生きてここから出られるみたいな口ぶりだね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:15.69,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Are you planning to make this a war zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.56,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ここを戦場にする気か
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:18.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:18.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の所為ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:21.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:21.89,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕が間違っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:23.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I selfishly thought that here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:28.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この場所だけは皆さんと立場を超えて会えるような気が勝手にしていました
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:28.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I could actually meet with you two \Nwithout having to consider my position.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:29.86,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Ango.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.93,0:18:29.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.75,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私の気が変わらないうちに消えるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:33.78,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Go before I change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:37.31,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,別に悲しんでいるんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.33,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I'm not sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:39.84,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,最初からわかっていたことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.91,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I knew this from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.18,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾が特務課であろうとなかろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.20,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Whether you were with the gifted \Nspecial operations division or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:46.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,失いたくないものは必ず失われる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:46.23,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,anything I would never want \Nto lose is always lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:49.55,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It is a given that everything \Nthat is worth wanting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:49.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,求める価値のあるものは皆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:53.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,手に入れた瞬間に失うことが約束されている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:53.24,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,will be lost the moment I obtain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:59.95,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,There's nothing worth pursuing at the \Ncost of prolonging a life of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:19:00.11,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,苦しい生を引き延ばしてまで追い求めるものなんて　何もない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:09.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Dazai-kun, Odasaku-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.15,0:19:09.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰君　織田作さん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:14.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,If there ever comes a time when the division\N and the Port Mafia don't exist
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:14.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いつか時代が変わって　特務課もポートマフィアもない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:18.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,我々がもっと自由な立場になったら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:18.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,and we all become freer men,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:19.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,またここ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:19.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,let's come back here and—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,云うな　安吾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:20.89,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Don't say it, Ango.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:25.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以上言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.53,0:19:25.10,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Don't say anything more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:26.81,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:27.03,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:29.40,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:29.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,親爺さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:34.81,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Kosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,幸介　克巳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:35.29,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Katsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:36.58,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.50,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,優　真嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:37.50,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Shinju!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.29,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:39.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,咲楽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.19,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,A map?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,地図
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:13.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,喉が痛かった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:13.26,Stray Dogs - Italics,O,0,0,0,,My throat hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.67,Stray Dogs - Italics,O,0,0,0,,I couldn't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:15.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,呼吸ができなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.58,Stray Dogs - Italics,O,0,0,0,,I heard someone screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:18.56,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かの叫び声が聞こえた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:26.38,Stray Dogs - Italics,O,0,0,0,,I realized, because my throat hurt so much, \Nthat I was the one who was screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:22.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりに喉が激しく痛むので気付いた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:26.31,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,叫んでいたのは　俺だった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:30.33,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,Then you write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:30.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ならばお前が書け
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:36.43,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Beard,0,0,0,,That's the only way you can \Nkeep that story perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:36.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それが唯一その小説を完璧なままにしておく方法だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:39.06,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I can't write it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:39.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もう書けない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:47.50,Stray Dogs - Default,O,0,0,0,,I can no longer write a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:43.68,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺はもう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.71,0:21:47.42,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,小説を書くことはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:09.85,sign_31802_310_Next_Time__Episo,Sign 2207,0,0,0,,Next Time: Episode 16 \N Bun{\c&HB78319&}go{\c&H000000&} Stray Dogs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.74,0:23:42.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だが違うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.38,0:23:46.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつはあまりに頭の切れるただの子供だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.64,0:23:49.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,暗闇の中で俺たちが見ている世界よりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.88,0:23:53.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,遥かに何もない虚無の世界で独り取り残され
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.59,0:23:55.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ泣いている子供だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.97,0:24:00.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今では　その孤独に土足で踏み込まなかったことを
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.24,0:24:02.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,少し後悔している
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:06.76,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,次回　文豪ストレイドッグス　第十六話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.21,0:24:09.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,文豪ストレイドッグ
